    HasCallbackScope, HasDataPoints, HasDataset, HasPointFillStrokeStyles, IsDefaultAnimationContainer, IsDefaultAnimationTransition, IsDefaultFillHandler, HasAnimationOptions, HasFill, HasSpanGaps
    public class StackedVerticalLineDataset
extends VerticalLineDataset
    The stacked vertical line chart allows a number of properties to be specified for each dataset.
    These are used to set display properties for a specific dataset.
    Extends the line dataset.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
